#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn2.20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.20:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Anāthapiṇḍikavagga "
msgstr "2. With Anāthapiṇḍika "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Anāthapiṇḍikasutta "
msgstr "20. With Anāthapiṇḍika "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn2.20:1.1"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi: "
msgstr "Standing to one side, the god Anāthapiṇḍika recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn2.20:2.1"
msgid "“Idañhi taṃ jetavanaṃ, "
msgstr "“This is indeed that Jeta’s Grove, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:2.2"
msgid "isisaṅghanisevitaṃ; "
msgstr "frequented by the Saṅgha of hermits, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:2.3"
msgid "Āvutthaṃ dhammarājena, "
msgstr "where the King of Dhamma stayed: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:2.4"
msgid "pītisañjananaṃ mama. "
msgstr "it brings me joy! "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.127, sc3
msgctxt "sn2.20:3.1"
msgid "Kammaṃ vijjā ca dhammo ca, "
msgstr "Deeds, knowledge, and principle; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:3.2"
msgid "sīlaṃ jīvitamuttamaṃ; "
msgstr "ethical conduct, an excellent livelihood; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:3.3"
msgid "Etena maccā sujjhanti, "
msgstr "by these are mortals purified, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:3.4"
msgid "na gottena dhanena vā. "
msgstr "not by clan or wealth. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn2.20:4.1"
msgid "Tasmā hi paṇḍito poso, "
msgstr "That’s why an astute person, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:4.2"
msgid "sampassaṃ atthamattano; "
msgstr "seeing what’s good for themselves, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:4.3"
msgid "Yoniso vicine dhammaṃ, "
msgstr "would examine the teaching rationally, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:4.4"
msgid "evaṃ tattha visujjhati. "
msgstr "and thus be purified in it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn2.20:5.1"
msgid "Sāriputtova paññāya, "
msgstr "Sāriputta has true wisdom, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:5.2"
msgid "sīlena upasamena ca; "
msgstr "ethics, and also peace. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:5.3"
msgid "Yopi pāraṅgato bhikkhu, "
msgstr "Any mendicant who has gone beyond "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:5.4"
msgid "etāvaparamo siyā”ti. "
msgstr "can at best equal him.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn2.20:6.1"
msgid "Idamavoca anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto. "
msgstr "This is what the god Anāthapiṇḍika said. "

msgctxt "sn2.20:6.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyi. "
msgstr "Then he bowed and respectfully circled the Buddha, keeping him on his right side, before vanishing right there. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn2.20:7.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā tassā rattiyā accayena bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then, when the night had passed, the Buddha addressed the mendicants: "

msgctxt "sn2.20:7.2"
msgid "“imaṃ, bhikkhave, rattiṃ aññataro devaputto abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, tonight, a certain glorious god, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, came to me, bowed, stood to one side, "

msgctxt "sn2.20:7.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho, bhikkhave, so devaputto mama santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi: "
msgstr "and recited these verses in my presence.” The Buddha then repeated the verses in full. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.128, sc8
msgctxt "sn2.20:8.1"
msgid "‘Idañhi taṃ jetavanaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:8.2"
msgid "isisaṅghanisevitaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:8.3"
msgid "Āvutthaṃ dhammarājena, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:8.4"
msgid "pītisañjananaṃ mama. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "sn2.20:9.1"
msgid "Kammaṃ vijjā ca dhammo ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:9.2"
msgid "sīlaṃ jīvitamuttamaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:9.3"
msgid "Etena maccā sujjhanti, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:9.4"
msgid "na gottena dhanena vā. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.56, sc10
msgctxt "sn2.20:10.1"
msgid "Tasmā hi paṇḍito poso, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:10.2"
msgid "sampassaṃ atthamattano; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:10.3"
msgid "Yoniso vicine dhammaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:10.4"
msgid "evaṃ tattha visujjhati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "sn2.20:11.1"
msgid "Sāriputtova paññāya, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:11.2"
msgid "sīlena upasamena ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:11.3"
msgid "Yopi pāraṅgato bhikkhu, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:11.4"
msgid "etāvaparamo siyā’ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "sn2.20:12.1"
msgid "Idamavoca, bhikkhave, so devaputto. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn2.20:12.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvā maṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyī”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc13
msgctxt "sn2.20:13.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, Venerable Ānanda said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn2.20:13.2"
msgid "“so hi nūna, bhante, anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto bhavissati. "
msgstr "“Sir, that god must surely have been Anāthapiṇḍika. "

msgctxt "sn2.20:13.3"
msgid "Anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati āyasmante sāriputte abhippasanno ahosī”ti. "
msgstr "For the householder Anāthapiṇḍika was devoted to Venerable Sāriputta.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.20:13.4"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, ānanda, yāvatakaṃ kho, ānanda, takkāya pattabbaṃ anuppattaṃ taṃ tayā. "
msgstr "“Good, good, Ānanda. You’ve reached the logical conclusion, as far as logic goes. "

msgctxt "sn2.20:13.5"
msgid "Anāthapiṇḍiko hi so, ānanda, devaputto”ti. "
msgstr "For that was indeed the god Anāthapiṇḍika.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn2.20:13.6"
msgid "Anāthapiṇḍikavaggo dutiyo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.129, sc14
#. VAR: Candimaso → candimāso (pts1, mr)
#. VAR: veṇḍu → veṇhu (bj, mr) | veṇhū (pts2)
msgctxt "sn2.20:14.1"
msgid "Candimaso ca veṇḍu ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:14.2"
msgid "Dīghalaṭṭhi ca nandano; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:14.3"
msgid "Candano vāsudatto ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:14.4"
msgid "Subrahmā kakudhena ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:14.5"
msgid "Uttaro navamo vutto, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.20:14.6"
msgid "Dasamo anāthapiṇḍikoti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
